  <summary date="2022-10-20T21:30:13Z" status="Introduced in House">Wild Horse and Burro Protection Act of 2022

This bill prohibits the Bureau of Land Management (BLM) from using or contracting for the use of helicopters or fixed-wing aircraft for gathering horses and burros under the Wild Free-roaming Horses and Burros Act. Further, BLM may not make contracts to use helicopters for transporting captured animals under such act.</summary>
